The Biggest Loser Australia - Families Season 10 Episode 04

Hosted by Fiona Falkiner, this season of TBL Families will see the trainers each paired with one Aussie family of four, as they motivate them to achieve their weight-loss dreams.

The first weigh-in proves to be very competitive with one contestant losing the most kilograms ever at this stage in the competition. Could this contestant be the one to watch?
